"NLLB-200 的多语言翻译模型，支持 200 种语言。使用 ONNX Runtime 进行设备端推理。" = "NLLB-200 multilingual model supporting 200 languages. ONNX Runtime for on-device inference.";
"VTM 是一款完全离线的语音翻译工具，支持实时语音识别、多语言翻译和语音合成。无需网络连接，所有数据处理均在本地完成，确保隐私安全。" = "VTM is a fully offline voice translator supporting real-time speech recognition, multilingual translation, and speech synthesis. All processing is local, ensuring privacy.";
"VTM 是一款语音翻译应用，允许用户通过语音输入进行实时翻译。我们保留随时修改或终止服务的权利，无需事先通知。" = "VTM is a voice translation app enabling real-time translation via voice input. We reserve the right to modify or discontinue the service at any time without notice.";
"VTM 语音翻译" = "VTM Voice Translator";
"VTM（以下简称"我们"）非常重视您的隐私保护。本隐私政策说明了我们如何收集、使用、存储和保护您的个人信息。使用本应用即表示您同意本政策的条款。" = "VTM ("we") values your privacy. This policy explains how we collect, use, store, and protect your personal information. By using this app, you agree to this policy.";
